                <story-points>
                  <story-point caption='Finding Optimal Regions for Victory:&#10;Based on the selected agent, map, and rank, this view shows the regions where players achieve the highest win rates. Regions are colour-coded for easy comparison. Insights from this map can guide players towards regions and strategies aligned with their strengths.' captured-sheet='Cq1' id='1' />
